{"tid":860691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「滴滴」供飲料 竟是司機尿 乘客誤喝","createTime":"2018-10-13T14:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T16:00:29.000Z","uid":80516,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"03c87219ea467ef9130baa416c40a8cf1d5f579e","tid":860691,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"港人北上乘坐公共交通工具時必須留神，不要亂飲車上飲品。內地日前有一名男子在上海乘坐「滴滴」網約車時，飲用了車內供乘客飲用的礦泉水，喝了一口才發現樽內裝的竟是司機的小便，且「還有溫度」。<br />\n<br />\n據內地傳媒報道，事發本月9日，到上海出差的孫姓事主，乘坐「滴滴禮橙專車」途中口渴，由於他知道專車是有提供乘客飲用水的，當看到司機位及副駕駛位中間飲品台放着一樽礦泉水，便拿起來喝，但發現樽蓋有些鬆動，便問司機「這樽水能喝嗎」？<br />\n<br />\n司機解釋可能是上一個乘客擰開但是沒喝，可以喝。孫男說因為當時車內光線較暗，自己也沒仔細看，只是看到樽身印有滴滴的標誌，就直接喝了，但入口後感覺不對，拿在手上「還有溫度」，才驚覺是尿，馬上吐出來。<br />\n<br />\n乘客感「還有溫度」<br />\n<br />\n孫男質問司機，司機還裝傻，當作甚麼都不知道。<br />\n<br />\n孫男決定報警，這時司機才開始瘋狂道歉，更承認瓶中的尿是自己的，因為深怕被投訴會令自己失業，想花錢和孫男私下和解。<br />\n<br />\n最終孫男下車，打電話向滴滴投訴及報警，及到醫院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n司機尿急用樽小便<br />\n<br />\n孫男表示，事後他自己嘔吐了一整天，一口飯沒吃，只有不停地喝酒抽煙。<br />\n<br />\n滴滴回應稱，涉事司機是因為內急找不到廁所，才使用礦泉水樽「解決」，之後將瓶子放置在司機位旁的飲品台，導致乘客誤飲。司機已因違規被封禁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/2018-10-11_23-35-42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F2018-10-11_23-35-42.jpg&h=b7819694&s={SIZE}\" />涉事「礦泉水」（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_news/%E6%BB%B4%E6%BB%B4%E4%BE%9B%E9%A3%B2%E6%96%99-%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%B0%BF-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E8%AA%A4%E5%96%9D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fmetro_news%2F%25E6%25BB%25B4%25E6%25BB%25B4%25E4%25BE%259B%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E6%2596%2599-%25E7%25AB%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25B0%25BF-%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%2596%259D%2F&d=nFMIurY5aehS8viB9UIe%2FIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=1c5644f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_news/%E6%BB%B4%E6%BB%B4%E4%BE%9B%E9%A3%B2%E6%96%99-%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%B0%BF-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E8%AA%A4%E5%96%9D/</a>"},{"pid":"3e0873b7c4e98a24aed9758b22c650b15d908341","tid":860691,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:09:41.000Z","msg":"物質豐富，足料"},{"pid":"46e32f1316f745bfb788f7bf6dbe0ee779058a57","tid":860691,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:11:31.000Z","msg":"沒事"},{"pid":"d94e0464a693cd669453b1c890c1957424fbc72c","tid":860691,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:35:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cc4e2129630ad84966942180bf560fab2f7a211","tid":860691,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e37dda8ac9b1d62aeecd51162ef7182c9ca71c6","tid":860691,"uid":22566,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc41c7227ee9304db6cbcf093bd4d0dc5c9ac06f","tid":860691,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:18:48.000Z","msg":"玩鳩你港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果然係大陸狗"},{"pid":"bf1fd9053178846f24875da7f68bdc94da079578","tid":860691,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:22:07.000Z","msg":"係大陸水我都未必敢亂飲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fa221835ac08bc88ab23e25b38b3deb8916581","tid":860691,"uid":128563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:27:05.000Z","msg":"尿其實俾個腎過濾過好乾淨吖，喺度扮咩撚嘢，奶閪嗰時又唔見咁大反應"},{"pid":"bb1c9d5c8ce6f51d0f66ae5fbb29efbe53ff799a","tid":860691,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15: